content.title: AI Assist
content.visibleText:
AI Assist

We believe in a tech-driven, AI-powered productivity expert with perfect memory whose sole mission is to make each interaction as smooth and as simple as possible with humans. Here, we focus on your needs.

Spiky/Differentiated Points of View

- AI can catch up on the user's workflow with very little user interaction.
- We want to be more than useful. We aim to deliver solutions that help us reach further into everyday human interactions.
- We want to seamlessly blend into your devices, phone lines, and text content and understand that the future of AI is not just about providing scripted replies. We take a leap into deeper learning, listening to the heart with our unique AI-driven solutions.
- Most of all, we believe in creating tools, products, and services that adapt, evolve, and respond to the challenges of tomorrow.
- The power of integrating AI into productivity with new workflows and adapt best practices, especially for knowledge workers.
- We consider our interaction with the AI Chatbot here as effortless and intuitive as possible, aiming at maximizing the engagement with our users in a direct and personal way.

Who are the users, and what outcome do they desire?

content.title: AI Assist
content.visibleText:
AI Assist

We believe in a tech-driven, AI-powered productivity system with perfect memory whose sole purpose is to make each interaction as valuable and as low-friction as possible. Here, we not only aim to provide high-quality, on-demand content but also to capture the nuances, hard to articulate thoughts, and the spiky/differentiated points of view.

Spiky/Differentiated Points of View

* AI can help us see what we wouldn't ordinarily see.
* We want to capture the nuances, hard to articulate thoughts.
* We want to see beauty, absurdity, in low-res phone videos, long text, and content and understand that these things tell us that we want without providing scripted lines. What we see and hear isn't a barrier to truth, but a path that guides us to create unique, relatable versions of the truth.
* The importance of listening to voices productively with workflows and about best practices, and about recognizing AI as the tech that is here to offer solutions and solve real-world problems.
* The current state of interaction with the AI in Clubhouse or other venues is limited just as we are, unable to see beyond the immediate and the obvious.

Who are the users, and what outcome do they desire?

content.visibleText:
AI Assist

We believe in a tech-rich, AI-powered productivity expert with perfect memory whose sole mission is to make everyone around them not only able to achieve more, but feel more fulfilled as they reach new heights.

Spikey/Differentiated Points of View

- AI can help us see what we wouldn't see via pattern detection.
- We want to be super helpful... We aim to deliver useful actions that help us each reach our new heights.
- We want to be really human, in our process flows, tone, and text content and understand that the best UX is one that feels personal.
- We use open-source libraries to keep our tech stack nimble and aligned with what the tech community finds valuable.
- We believe that the future of AI is not in hard math problems or scripted roles. We take a human-first approach to design, focusing on usability and providing easy-to-use interfaces.
- The power of technologies to improve productivity with new workflows and adapt best practices, keeping businesses and individuals ahead of the curve.
- We consider our role in working with the AI tech that is iterative and nimble just as important as any macro AI strategy.

Who are the users, and what outcome do they desire?
